6321.desc:
Dear Doctors: 

Recently, some players have been sharing personal social accounts or selling in-game resources in our chat channel; Celia advises all doctors not to add strangers' social accounts and to protect your personal information. The purchasable packs are officially priced.

If you need more Diamonds to upgrade buildings or purchase items, the only authorized way to buy them is through your own account within the game. 

If you want more resource rewards, follow our official community account for generous rewards.

Thank you for your support and understanding, enjoy the game; 

Last Asylum Team;

8200101.activityInstruction:
Easter Egg Hunt, tap for endless excitement!

Event Rules:
1. The event lasts for 7 days, with a new pack unlocked daily. Each pack purchase grants a Golden Hammer;
2. Use a Golden Hammer to tap an egg and randomly win exciting prizes;
3. There are 7 exciting prizes in total, all of which can be won;
4. Prizes already obtained will not be repeated;
5. Open the Easter Egg Hunt daily to receive free revival gifts;
6. Unused Golden Hammer taps during the event will be lost after it ends.

8100101.activityInstruction:
1. During the event, you must choose daily rewards before purchasing Weekly Specials;
2. Daily rewards cannot be changed when the purchase becomes effective;
3. After the event starts, one reward claim is unlocked per day. If you purchase a pack on the last day, you can claim all rewards for the days. Unclaimed rewards will be sent via mail;
4. After the event ends, unclaimed Weekly Specials (including daily rewards not claimed after purchase) will be sent via mail;
5. Weekly Special II can only be purchased after buying Weekly Special I.
